comments.body:
@dagdagdag83 what part of service meshes do you see relevant here? 
Is it the provisioning part (e.g. Envoy SDS) or the usage part (sidecar establishing mutual TLS). Do you feel like we should cover service meshes only in the context of K8S or also wider (incl. VM, etc.). 

If it's the provisioning part, we believe we have that already covered with "Local API" pattern.
